<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ ṣkẖrẗ ạldhwr qd ḍrbt mn ạ̉jly</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yā ṣakẖ̊raẗa ạldũhūri qad̊
 ḍurib̊ta min̊ ạảj̊lī
 litaf̊taḥa ạl̊bāba ạlãdẖī
 yad̊kẖuluhu mitẖ̊lī

[V2]
 2- fadamuka ạlzãkī̃ lidẖā
 min̊ jan̊bika sāla
 wah̊wa ạlãdẖī qad̊ ṭahãra
 ại̹tẖ̊mī walaẘ ṭāla

[V3]
 3- bidamika ạsẖ̊taraẙtanā
 ạảʿ̊ṭaẙtanā ạl̊kẖalạṣ̊
 lidẖā ạʿ̊tamad̊nā biạs̊mika
 waṣir̊nā sẖaʿ̊baⁿạ kẖāṣ̃

[V4]
 4- qadi ạḥ̊tamal̊ta waḥ̊daka
 ạlậlạama wālṣãlīb̊
 wālậna laka waḥ̊daka
 ạlại̹k̊rāmu yā ḥabīb̊</lyrics>
</song>